## Account Center Build Plan

A protected `/account/*` section with 5 pages, header dropdown, and a shared sidebar/tab nav.

### 1. Database migration (show first, apply on approval)

New table `connection_waitlist`:
- `id uuid PK default gen_random_uuid()`
- `user_id uuid not null` (references auth.users via RLS check, no FK to auth.users)
- `platform text not null check (platform in ('instagram','tiktok','youtube','facebook'))`
- `created_at timestamptz default now()`
- `unique(user_id, platform)`
- RLS: select/insert own rows (`user_id = auth.uid()`)

### 2. Header dropdown
Update the existing app header (in `src/routes/app.tsx` or shared header component â€” will inspect first):
- Add an avatar circle (initial from `display_name`) left of the name
- Wrap in `DropdownMenu` from `@/components/ui/dropdown-menu`
- 5 nav items + divider + Sign out (reuses existing signOut)

### 3. Shared `/account` layout
Create `src/routes/account.tsx` as a layout route:
- Auth gate in `beforeLoad` (redirect to `/login` if no session)
- Renders the same app header (extract into `src/components/AppHeader.tsx` so `/app` and `/account/*` share it)
- Sidebar nav (200px) on desktop, sticky horizontal tabs on mobile
- `<Outlet />` for child pages

