### 5. Routing notes
- TanStack file-based: `account.tsx` (layout) + `account.index.tsx`, `account.history.tsx`, etc.
- All wrapped via auth check in the layout `beforeLoad`
- Sidebar built with simple `<Link activeProps={{...}}>` (no shadcn Sidebar provider needed â€” simpler and matches request)

### 6. Reuse / no-touch
- Will NOT modify any existing card components or `/app` page logic
- Will extract header into `AppHeader.tsx` and update `/app` to use it (minor, no behavior change beyond adding the dropdown)

